\"><strong>一、单词的记忆方法和原理</strong></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">1、联想法&mdash;&mdash;发音，拆分（拼音），故事，进行记忆</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\" />\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">适合大部分初中单词</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\" />\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">2、词根 词缀</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\" />\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">适合高中单词 大学四六级单词 &nbsp;托福雅思单词</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\" />\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;我们应该把二者结合，从已知到未知</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px