t-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">规律总结：</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\" />\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">（1）中文&mdash;&mdash;发音相似，意思不同</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\" />\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">英文&mdash;&mdash;发音不同，意思相似或者完全相反</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\" />\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">（2）前缀的作用&mdash;&mdash;方向，否定，加强语气</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\" />\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">词根的作用&mdash;&mdash;意义</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\" />\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">后缀的作用&mdash;&