 font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\" />\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">其实词根被分开了，导致词根很多</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\" />\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">完全可以写成 vis=vid=看=visit video&hellip;&hellip;</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\" />\n\t<span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">所以我们需要将词根相似的在一起记忆</span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\" />\n\t<br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\" />\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>三、你应该知道一些词汇构词法则</strong></span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\" />\n\t<span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Wen