iragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\" />\n\t<br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\" />\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 127, 229);\">2、</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 127, 229);\">单词的大突破&mdash;&mdash;词根详细讲解，一次记住<br />\n\t</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">干货讲解回复可见（PS：想要获得最直观感受可以讲以下笔记与老师上课视频结合起来学习哦）</span></p>\n<div class=\"pnl_replyCantView_content\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">词根&nbsp;bond &nbsp;捆，绑，债券；结合<br />\n\t\t<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201503/eac3c3c4-233e-472a-8c6e-6794665f4b0d.png\" /><br />\n\t\t后缀 &nbsp;age （名称后缀）人和物<br />\n\t\t<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201503/eb75b169-6d6b-40a6-91c1-73327d315807.png\" /><br />\n\t\t</span></p>\n\t<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">词根&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 1.8;\">min-men 小</span></span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201503/b9c642ec-fe87-4