  "link": "http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p723340/", 
  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p723340/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t</p>\n<p>\n\tMr Been appears in this scene belongs to the movie &quot;Love Actually&quot;, he always so funny.片段选自《真爱至上》，憨豆先生出现在了这个场景里，他总是那么逗。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>完整台词对白：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t- Looking for anything in particular, sir?</p>\n<p>\n\t- Yes, um- That <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/necklace\" target=\"_blank\">necklace</a> there. How much is it?</p>\n<p>\n\t- lt's &pound;270.</p>\n<p>\n\t- Um, all right. Uh,<u>l'll have it</u><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">①</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">.</span></p>\n<p>\n\t- Lovely.</p>\n<p>\n\t- Would you like it... <u>gift-wrapped</u><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">②</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">?</span></p>\n<p>\n\t- Uh, yes. All right.</p>\n<p>\n\t- Lovely.</p>\n<p>\n\t- Let me just <u>pop it</u><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">③&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">in the box. There.</span></p>\n<p>\n\t- Look, could we be quite quick?</p>\n<p>\n\t- Certainly, sir. Ready <u>in the flashiest of flashes</u><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">④</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">. There.</span></p>\n<p>\n\t- It's great.</p>\n<p>\n\t- <u>Not quite finished</u><span style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">⑤</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">.</span></p>\n<p>\n\t- Look, actually, l-l don't need a bag. l'll just put it in my pocket.</p>\n<p>\n\t- Oh, this isn't a bag, sir.</p>\n<p>\n\t- Really?</p>\n<p>\n\t- This is so much more than a bag. Ooh!</p>\n<p>\n\t- Could we be quite quick, please?</p>\n<p>\n\t-&nbsp;<a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Prontissimo\" target=\"_blank\">Prontissimo</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">⑥</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">.</span></p>\n<p>\n\t- What's that?</p>\n<p>\n\t- It's a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/cinnamon\" target=\"_blank\">cinnamon</a> stick, sir.</p>\n<p>\n\t- Actually, l really, uh, can't wait.</p>\n<p>\n\t- Oh, you won't regret it, sir.</p>\n<p>\n\t- <u>Wanna bet</u><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">⑦</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">?</span></p>\n<p>\n\t- <u>'Tis</u><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">⑧&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">but the work of a moment.</span></p>\n<p>\n\t- There we are. Almost finished<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">.</span></p>\n<p>\n\t- Almost finished? What else's gonna be? Are you gonna dip it in yogurt? Cover it with <u>chocolate buttons</u><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">⑨</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">?</span></p>\n<p>\n\t- Oh, no, sir. We're going to pop it in the Christmas box.</p>\n<p>\n\t- But I don't want a Christmas box.</p>\n<p>\n\t- But you said you wanted it gift-wrapped.</p>\n<p>\n\t- l did, but...</p>\n<p>\n\t-This is the final <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/flourish\" target=\"_blank\">flourish</a>.</p>\n<p>\n\t- Can I just pay?</p>\n<p>\n\t- All we need now...</p>\n<p>\n\t- Oh, God!</p>\n<p>\n\t- ...is a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/sprig\" target=\"_blank\">sprig</a> of <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/holly\" target=\"_blank\">holly</a>.</p>\n<p>\n\t- No. No. No. No. No <u>bloody</u><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">⑩&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">holly.</span></p>\n<p>\n\t- But, sir, the...</p>\n<p>\n\t- Leave it, leave it, just leave it.</p>\n<p>\n\t- Ooh, <u>loitering</u><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">⑪&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">around the jewellery section, I see.</span></p>\n<p>\n\t- No, I was just looking around, you know.</p>\n<p>\n\t- Don&rsquo;t worry. My expectations are not <u>that high</u><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">⑫&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">after thirteen years of </span><u style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Mr. Oh-But-You-Always-Love-Scarves</u><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">⑬</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">. Actually, </span><u style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">I do love them</u><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">⑭</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">.</span></p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>台词语言点讲解：<br />\n\t</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">①I&rsquo;LL HAVE IT：买东西的时候和店员说&ldquo;爷要了&rdquo;就这么表达。不过你分得清will和going to的区别吗？</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">说到做决定的时候，我们用will表达做决定的那瞬间；</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">当我们表达&ldquo;已经做下了这个决定&rdquo;，则用going to。所以我们买东西的时候，我决定买某件物品了，我们要说&ldquo;I&rsquo;ll have it.&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t例句：</p>\n<p>\n\t- What would you like to drink?</p>\n<p>\n\t- I don&rsquo;t know, maybe a coke? Or&hellip; ok, no, I&rsquo;ll have a beer.</p>\n<p>\n\t---------------------------</p>\n<p>\n\t- So where are you going for your holidays this summer?</p>\n<p>\n\t- We&rsquo;re going to visit Andalucia, in southern Spain. We were planning to go to Turkey but then we saw a documentary about Andalucia on TV and changed our plans. We&rsquo;re leaving on July the 3rd.</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">②</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">GIFT-WRAPPED：礼物包装</span></p>\n<p>\n\t③口语表达：POP IT=put it, place it.</p>\n<p>\n\t④In the flashinest of flashes：表达速度很快很快。<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">如果你做某事&rdquo;in a flash&rdquo;，表示你做的很快；所以说这句话表达的其实就是in a flash的最高级，表示做事很快很快。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t⑤Not quite finished：几乎完成了，但是差那么一点点。</p>\n<p>\n\t⑥PRONTISSIMO= (意大利语) Very quickly，很快。</p>\n<p>\n\t⑦口语表达Wanna bet？（你想打个赌吗？）这是一种非常口语化的表达，在你不同意某人的预测时使用。</p>\n<p>\n\t例句：</p>\n<p>\n\t- Enjoy your trip and don&rsquo;t be so pessimistic, everything&rsquo;s going to be great!</p>\n<p>\n\t- Wanna bet? = I don&rsquo;t agree, I think things won&rsquo;t be great.</p>\n<p>\n\t⑧&lsquo;TIS= It is.通常It is的缩写是it&rsquo;s，但是有时你会听到英式英语说&rsquo;tis。这种缩写在旧式英语中很常见，如今在诗歌和很多英国方言里还能听到。<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">比如&rsquo;tis but=It&rsquo;s only</span></p>\n<p>\n\t⑨Chocolate buttons：巧克力小饼干（纽扣型），通常撒蛋糕上。</p>\n<p>\n\t⑩Bloody：骂人的词，有点粗鲁。</p>\n<p>\n\t⑪Loitering：to loiter就是漫无目的随便转转，或站着的意思，比如你说在等人的时候就可以这么说。</p>\n<p>\n\t⑫口语表达that high=so high, very high</p>\n<p>\n\t⑬Mr. Oh-but-you-always-love-scarves：这是一种很常见的口语表达，用来以某种特征来定义某人。举个例子：</p>\n<p>\n\t- Hello, Mr. Sorry-I&rsquo;m-Late=你是在暗指他老是迟到，所以他总说：&ldquo;Sorry, I&rsquo;m late&rdquo;。这样称呼对方其实有责备的意味。</p>\n<p>\n\t- Yes, she is Miss Everything&rsquo;s-Ok = 这里你就是暗指她是那种&ldquo;永远看不到问题（everything is ok）&rdquo;的人。</p>\n<p>\n\t⑭I DO LOVE THEM= I really love them. 在肯定疑问句（affirmative question）里用do表示强调动词。</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px;\">声明：本文系沪江英语独家供稿，转载请注明出处。代表作者个人观点，仅供参考。如有不妥之处，欢迎指正。</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p723340/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p723340\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723235/\">看电影学英文:《小黄人大电影》学习笔记</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723074/\">励志活字典:51岁女教师2年背完22万单词</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723320/\">1分钟讲26个英文笑话 打破吉尼斯世界纪录</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723200/\">脸书CEO扎克伯格的推荐书单</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723104/\">英国人教你记单词：22万词汇so easy！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723307/\">张艺谋新片《长城》:当马特达蒙遭遇TFBOYS</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p722685/\">记得那时年纪小，你爱谈天我爱笑</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723105/\">中外最强毒舌: 该不该买苹果表</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723228/\">点击223万监控实拍: 骑车老太神避让躲车祸 </a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723317/\">结婚不容易，用对“marry”更不容易</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
